Best Friend, all main fonts: http://www.gust.org.pl/projects/e-foundry
GUST Foundry fonts begin with
- LM ...
- Tex Gyre ...
...These cover most main typefaces and are free viz http://www.gust.org.pl/fonts/licenses/GUST-FONT-LICENSE.txt

More fonts: https://www.fontsquirrel.com

copy fonts to ~/.fonts
run: fc-cache -f -v

